 X(g(Y,Z)) = \nabla_X g (Y,Z) = \nabla g (X,Y,Z) 
\nabla^{LC}_X g (Y,Z) = 0
 \nabla_X g (Y,Z) = \nabla^{LC}_X g (Y,Z) - g(S(X,Y),Z) - g(Y,S(X,Z)) 
 \nabla_X g (Y,Z) = - g(S(X,Y),Z) - g(Y,S(X,Z)) 
